rows.label: qst202909_msg0001
rows.name: Meh-meh-meh-mehhhh!!!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0002
rows.name: Wh-what the heck?!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0003
rows.name: Me thought me would die...!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0004
rows.name: Thanks friends much for saving!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0005
rows.name: Well, that sure ain't Kastina.

rows.label: qst202909_msg0006
rows.name:
Who the heck are you, anyway?
And what're you doing here?

rows.label: qst202909_msg0007
rows.name:
Friends should call me Sage!
Just Sage!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0008
rows.name:
Me is in training to become
great Nopon Sage!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0009
rows.name:
Was in such deep meditation, did not
notice when snow pile up on top of me.
Almost became Nopon Icicle!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0010
rows.name:
But me feel like me has achieved new
level of enlightenment from experience.

rows.label: qst202909_msg0011
rows.name: Even for a Nopon, this guy's weird...

rows.label: qst202909_msg0012
rows.name:
Still, if he's been around here,
he might know something.
We gotta find out where Kastina went.

rows.label: qst202909_msg0013
rows.name:
Listen, did you see a Luxurian girl
around here? We heard she was
comin' over this way.

rows.label: qst202909_msg0014
rows.name: Meh-meh... Luxurian girl...?

rows.label: qst202909_msg0015
rows.name:
Feel like may have seen...
Or maybe not...

rows.label: qst202909_msg0016
rows.name:
Give us a straight answer, wouldja?
Her life might be on the line here!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0017
rows.name: Meh-meh...

rows.label: qst202909_msg0018
rows.name:
If friends give offering of food,
maybe it help me remember!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0020
rows.name: Seriously? That's your deal here?

rows.label: qst202909_msg0021
rows.name:
Me is very hungry!
Not having strength to think!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0022
rows.name:
If stomach full, probably remember
all about girl who come here!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0023
rows.name:
Sounds mighty suspicious if
you ask me, but I guess if that's
what it takes...

rows.label: qst202909_msg0024
rows.name: Go on then, what're you after?

rows.label: qst202909_msg0025
rows.name:
Me craving Juicy Ray Fin
and Benign Cricket!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0026
rows.name: Oh, also Soft Sea Cucumber!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0027
rows.name: Me wait right here for offerings!

rows.label: qst202909_msg0028
rows.name: Kastina!
